game.name: Arty Mouse Coloring Book
game.description:
Hey boys and girls! Do you love coloring and animals? Luckily, we have got you covered with a brand new arcade challenge where you will get a lovely digital coloring book that is specially designed for kids. Does not it look pretty exciting and challenging? Join Arty Mouse & Friends Coloring Book game and be prepared to color multiple interesting characters from the huge Arty Mouse universe! This cute coloring puzzle is also suitable for parents and pre-school institutions.  

There are multiple templates, brush sizes and colors to play through. You will get a chance to color different popular characters including Spiro the snail, Rainbow Birds, Dot the bear, Stripy the cat, and Scribble the dog. Things look easy, but lots of complex challenges will be there to deal with when you move further. You can increase or decrease the size of your brush while looking forward to finish new HTML5 coloring game. Once you complete the colors, click on the done button and see the final result on the screen.  

Take your creativity and coloring imagination skill to the next level when you try out this cool online animal game! You would be amazed to meet with special animals and coloring book pictures and get a pleasure of having a great time. No matter which age group you belong to, the funny and engaging environment of the gameplay will be able to keep you glued to the screen for long. Browse through our extensive and fine collection of free animal games to get some more quality time online without download!
